WEBVTT

00:12:26.791 --> 00:12:30.084
that understands the emotional
impact of language,

00:12:30.108 --> 00:12:31.568
we can build empathy.

00:12:31.592 --> 00:12:34.017
That means that we can have
dialogue between people

00:12:34.041 --> 00:12:35.857
with different politics,

00:12:35.881 --> 00:12:37.097
different worldviews,

00:12:37.121 --> 00:12:38.367
different values.

00:12:39.359 --> 00:12:44.134
And we can reinvigorate the spaces online
that most of us have given up on.

00:12:45.857 --> 00:12:49.642
When people use technology
to exploit and harm others,

00:12:49.666 --> 00:12:53.308
they're preying on our human fears
and vulnerabilities.

00:12:54.461 --> 00:12:57.969
If we ever thought
that we could build an internet

00:12:57.993 --> 00:13:00.571
insulated from the dark side of humanity,